nodeList.name: Facial Expression Detection
nodeList.description: Detect facial expressions of people using this effect. To detect facial expression more than one face, assign a Face Expression Detection node to each face in the scene. It can detect up to five facial expressions.

property.value: Detect facial expressions of people using this effect. To detect facial expression more than one face, assign a Face Expression Detection node to each face in the scene. It can detect up to five facial expressions.

owner.name: Facial Movement Detection
owner.description: Detect the movement on face. Each movement has four states: Begin, Stay, End, and None. For movement such as eye blink, even the fastest blink has one frame "Stay" state. To detect facial movement more than one face, assign a Face Movement Detection node to each face in the scene. It can detect up to five facial movements.
